---
title: Jamaican Chicken & Coconut-Spinach Rice with Caramelised Pineapple Salsa
description: Caribbean spice is such a party for your mouth that we had to step up every element of this lively dish, from the pineapple salsa to the coconut-spinach rice. If you or the kids like things mild, just leave out the chilli – the salsa is already packed with flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5f05402fcd9cfd006c41643f-23617d6c.jpg
